1. "sudo pacman -S alsa-utils pulseaudio pulseaudio-alsa pavucontrol" 
-> first 3 to enable audio, 4rth to have tray icon for sound and volume control.
2. reboot...
3. type "alsamixer" in terminal
4. press "m" if you see "MM" (surrounded by black),
don't press anything if you see "OO" (sorrounded by green),
use arrows to change volume strength.

